<p>Go to <strong>Setup » Assistants » Omni-Channel</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Base settings - Amazon</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Open the assistant for the Amazon account.<br>
→ The assistant opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings as described in <a href="#assistant-base-settings">Table 1</a>.</p>
</li>
