<div class="paragraph">
<p>Carry out the following settings before you activate the export for a new catalogue.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Settings in the setup menu:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Setup » Markets » Amazon » Settings</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the Amazon account.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings described in <a href="#assistant-menu">Table 2</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> (<span class="icon green"><i class="fa fa-save  "></i></span>) the settings.</p>
</li>
